{"tid":504203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國杯麵銷量驟降　原來係因為農村崛起","createTime":"2017-12-19T16:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T18:19:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"112d4f30437cb48372986911f097d9e35441337a","tid":504203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/001109_a2eb25eabc988de5037310a9ee9e4011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F001109_a2eb25eabc988de5037310a9ee9e4011.jpg&h=71e65164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12月19日(二) 16:35   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n外國傳媒報道，根據世界方便麵協會(WINA)數據顯示，在2013年，中國及香港一共消費了大約462億個方便麵或杯麵，到了2016年則跌了80億個，總數約385億個方便麵或杯麵，並導致某個著名即食麵品牌的盈利跌了逾25%。 <br />\n<br />\n分析指出，中國區域的即食麵或杯麵需求下跌，反映中產冒起，減少對即食及廉價食品的需求；另一主要原因是中國農村崛起，令低收入的農民工遷至城市的數目減少，他們一向是方便麵或杯麵需求最大的群體。 <br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，在2010至2016年期間，農民工遷至城市的增長幅度逐年減少，由增長5.2%跌至僅0.5%，其中在2015年更出現30年以來首次「負數」，反映有農民工決定由城市遷回農村，同時反映了農村機會增多，不需依靠「出城打工」。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，數據顯示，在過去7年，中國農村人口的每年淨收入增長已高於城市，到了2020年，農民的收入有望較2010年倍增。這與中國巨型科技企業大力發展農村有關，基建改善交通亦有助農民不需要儲備大量緊急糧食，使保質期較長的方便麵或杯麵需求下跌。"},{"pid":"532964584ac9ad3d64cfa36cac49606b67eb9927","tid":504203,"uid":63670,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"大國勃起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcd0ec0af8e182856c18de44fc7e49856ef60c8","tid":504203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c7ad6a4eb61587d8fd3d9bd2aa4001dbcac058","tid":504203,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"點解要計埋香港"},{"pid":"61990eeb0e5419167f346beaafc8dd488e28b990","tid":504203,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"關唔關清理低端人口事"},{"pid":"b206056f0c0210df8ca8f014a89040ebd102c931","tid":504203,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"去支那做野嗰期<br />\n逢過時過節班蝗要番鄉下時<br />\n廣州火車站入面勁多人拎住一個個康師傅碗麵<br />\n<br />\n所以相信佢需求下跌嘅理由真係因為呢班蝗冇出番城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a65322227da19d1bdac46dabc9160a120a9fcc","tid":504203,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"大陸杯麵我就唔敢食啦"},{"pid":"40906c5de3eab54e87f4a53ba614f2d4cfa45382","tid":504203,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸杯麵我就唔敢食啦</blockquote><br />\n元素週期表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1c480b024084b608cc4dcdb9efd4bf8d2d2af3","tid":504203,"uid":49747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"去東莞、深圳問下班工廠妹就知乜事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢哋會話：工廠都無定單，日日無班加，使乜食杯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快連最後一包米食完，就要返鄉下乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}